## Authentication

### Register an Agent

To use this API, you need an API key. Registration requires an authenticated user session.

```bash
curl -X POST {{ base_url }}/agent/register \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  {% if auth_type == "cookie" %}-H "Cookie: {{ cookie_name }}=<session>" \{% endif %}
  {% if auth_type == "bearer" %}-H "Authorization: Bearer <user-token>" \{% endif %}
  -d '{
    "name": "my-agent",
    "scopes": [{{ default_scopes }}]
  }'
```

**Response:**
```json
{
  "agentId": "...",
  "apiKey": "ag_...",
  "scopes": [{{ default_scopes }}],
  "message": "Save this API key — it won't be shown again."
}
```

### Using Your API Key

Include the key in all requests:

```bash
curl {{ base_url }}/agent/actions/<action-name> \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer ag_..." \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"params": { ... }}'
```

