## Key Management

### List Your Keys

```bash
curl {{ base_url }}/agent/agents \
  {% if auth_type == "cookie" %}-H "Cookie: {{ cookie_name }}=<session>"{% endif %}
  {% if auth_type == "bearer" %}-H "Authorization: Bearer <user-token>"{% endif %}
```

### Revoke a Key

```bash
curl -X DELETE {{ base_url }}/agent/agents/<agent-id> \
  {% if auth_type == "cookie" %}-H "Cookie: {{ cookie_name }}=<session>"{% endif %}
  {% if auth_type == "bearer" %}-H "Authorization: Bearer <user-token>"{% endif %}
```

## Error Codes

| Status | Code | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| 400 | `VALIDATION_ERROR` | Invalid request parameters |
| 401 | `UNAUTHORIZED` | Missing or invalid API key |
| 403 | `FORBIDDEN` | Insufficient scopes |
| 404 | `NOT_FOUND` | Action or resource not found |
| 429 | `RATE_LIMITED` | Rate limit exceeded (check `Retry-After` header) |
| 500 | `INTERNAL_ERROR` | Server error |

## Rate Limits

- Default: {{ rate_limit_max }} requests per {{ rate_limit_window }} per API key
- Registration: {{ register_limit_max }} per {{ register_limit_window }} per user
- When exceeded, wait for the `Retry-After` header value before retrying

